{"word":"H6544 - פָּרַע - pâraʻ - paw-rah' - Avenge","slug":"H6544","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">פָּרַע</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>pâraʻ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>paw-rah'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Avenge"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E4;&#x05BC;&#x05E8;&#x05E2; - pa&#x0302;ra&#x201B;</b> - <i>paw-rah'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>loosen</i>; by implication to <i>expose</i>, <i>dismiss</i>; figuratively <i>absolve</i>, <i>begin: - </i>avenge, avoid, bare, go back, let, (make) naked, set at nought, perish, refuse, uncover."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H6547\">H6547</a>, <a href=\"#/H6550\">H6550</a>, <a href=\"#/H6551\">H6551</a>, <a href=\"#/H6554\">H6554</a>"}]}